ygData.messageBody:
Hello guys... can someone help me out with my Singtel Magix
problems? I just got it, and I can't seem to get into the EQ login
server. I always get stuck after entering my password, as if the
server was down.

Moreover, the patch server update screen (during EQ startup)
doesn't work always work the first time... I will get an error the first
time, and only on the 2nd try will I get in. The optional update patch
never works, though. I will always get the standard error message.

Seems like a problem with my network configs, but I've played
around with it, disabling everything except TCP/IP drivers, etc, but
no luck.

I need some help. Everything else works fine, mailing, browsing,
ICQ... all ok. Only EQ... Aaarrgggghhh!


--


Love is in the air...
Get me a gas mask, quick!!!

Cya,
Praetor
